snippet.textDisplay:
Jen's 2nd marriage to Justin Thoroux lasted only 2 years. I read an alleged report that the one big reason that had a huge impact in ending that marriage was when Thoroux stumbled across some old post-it love notes from Brad to Jen during their relationship she apparently kept. Of course it only added his jealousy to the list of their issues. Now if this is a true fact that Jennifer held on to some old Brad love notes, we might ask WHY and what for. Did she forget she still had them? You'd think most scorned exes would do a better cleaning job in ridding old memories of the past.
This was posted on Showbiz CheatSheet Feb.26, 2018, so anyone can cherry-pick what they choose to believe or not from it , yet the rumored love notes compelled me to add up why Jen's forgiveness when he done her such unforgivable dirt , why the reuniting with this deceitful cheating man, accepting him at her 50th birthday party., her Christmas party, inviting more than "just friends" gestures with him at the SAG with smiles that had Hollywood celebrities spellbound ? Are constant rumors of their frequent communications just rumors? If so, these two acting celebrities have played the best acting role parts of their entire careers.

snippet.textDisplay: Well clearly Jennifer is a strong beautiful woman who can forgive and move on because she knows her life is the better for doing so!  She can be kind and even still have some remnants of love for Brad and that's okay BUT doesn't necessarily mean that she is ready to go down that lane again!  I think Brad has had to go thru some tough life challenging lessons that stopped him from continually falling off of fools mountain!  I think NOW when he looks at her he realizes the colossal mistake he made and what a gem of a lady and wife he did not appreciate because of all the stuff going on in his head!  I think that is why they can truly have a healthy friendship now because he FINALLY GETS IT......better late than never!!!!  Jennifer would have a lot of Brad baggage to juggle should she decide to go back down that lane and only she can determine IF it's worth it for her peace of mind!!!!  JUST MY HUMBLE OPINION.... BUT HEY WHAT DO I KNOW, IJS!!!!  LOL!!!
